You can create your own cookie to save the server generated 
information in clients machine.

To create a Cookie object you need to call the Cookie constructor.
And need to supply the name and value information.

Because Cookie is just a name - value pair information generated by serever 
to send to a client with an intention to get back the information on each 
subsequent request. The name and value must be String.

To add a cookie use addCookie() method of response object.

To get back the cookie from the client use the getCookies() method of request object.


